==English==
'''Pericope'''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A section of text, especially of scripture. 

Gk: "section"

The reader looked up the Sunday morning '''pericope'''.

The oldest know system of '''pericopes''' in the Western Church is ascribed to Jerome.

